OL,3,C'Love told through music': Bradley
OL,4,CCooper talks new biopic 'Maestro'
OL,6,FSo popular are biopics, it is perhaps
OL,7,Fsurprising it's taken so long for one
OL,8,Fto be made about Leonard Bernstein.
OL,10,FA humanitarian, an author, a teacher
OL,11,F- if, it seems, hardly a saintly
OL,12,Fhusband. In any case, it was for his
OL,13,Fmusic that Bernstein will always be
OL,14,Fbest remembered.
OL,16,FHe is seen as one of the most
OL,17,Fsignificant composers of the 20th
OL,18,FCentury. A tall order, then, for
OL,19,FBradley Cooper to portray the
OL,20,F'Maestro' in his new Netflix film.
